      <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS123"/>
      <p><a href="ch71s15.html#MonstersS123">Sprites</a> are reclusive fey. They go out of their way to fight evil and ugliness and to protect their homelands. Combat<a href="img/MonstersS.Sprite.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersS.Sprite.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p><a href="ch71s15.html#MonstersS123">Sprites</a> fight their opponents with spell-like abilities and pintsized weaponry. They prefer ambushes and other trickery over direct confrontation.</p>
      <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage"/>
        <a name="id2194934"/>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
          <div class="keyword">other</div>
        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS124"/>
