        <p><a href="ch71s15.html#MonstersS125">Grigs</a> can leap great distances. They have light blue skin, forest-green hair, and brown hairy legs, and usually wear tunics or brightly colored vests with buttons made from tiny gems. A <a href="ch71s15.html#MonstersS125">grig</a> stands 1-1/2 feet tall and weighs about 1 pound.</p>
        <p><a href="ch71s15.html#MonstersS125">Grigs</a> speak Sylvan. Some also speak Common.</p>
        <div class="sect4" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage">
