          <p><a href="ch71s15.html#MonstersS125">Grigs</a> are fierce by <a href="ch71s15.html#MonstersS123">sprite</a> standards, attacking opponents fearlessly with bow and dagger.</p>
          <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
