            </div>
            <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS127"/>
            <p><span class="strong"><strong>Spell-Like Abilities:</strong></span> 3/day-<span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch45.html#SpellsD-E37">disguise self</a></em></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch45.html#SpellsD-E66">entangle</a></em></span> (DC 13)<span class="emphasis"><em/></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch47.html#SpellsH-L52">invisibility</a></em></span> (self only), <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch49.html#SpellsP-R44">pyrotechnics</a></em></span> (DC 14)<span class="emphasis"><em/></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch51.html#SpellsT-Z34">ventriloquism</a></em></span> (DC 13)<span class="emphasis"><em/></span>. Caster level 9th. The save DCs are Charisma-based.</p>
