            <p><span class="strong"><strong>Fiddle (Su):</strong></span> One <a href="ch71s15.html#MonstersS125">grig</a> in each band carries a tiny, grig-sized fiddle. When the fiddler plays, any nonsprite within 30 feet of the instrument must succeed on a DC 12 Will save or be affected as though by <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch47.html#SpellsH-L59">irresistible dance</a></em></span> for as long as the playing continues. The save DC is Charisma-based.</p>
