            <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS129"/>
            <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> <a href="ch71s15.html#MonstersS125">Grigs</a> have a +8 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills192">Jump</a> checks. *They also have a +5 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills211">Move Silently</a> checks in a forest setting.</p>
